channel.description: Okay, so I've been trying to setup a server again but this time around I'm failing twice as hard as in 2009, aha, and was wondering if someone could be of help? i'm interested in the deltascape source, and already have one downloaded. I've done the no-ip port forwarding so that should be covered. whats the next steps? I want to start learning java coding so this might be a good start. For people that are experienced coders feel free to pm me your msn ill be happy to discuss this more with someone who works with java well.
